Wrapper function for LENS_K\n * @param proj object containing lens distortion parameters (k1, k2, k3)\n * @param r2 radial distance\n * @returns The distortion factor\n */\nfunction LENS(proj: GeoProj, r2: number): number {\n  return LENS_K(proj.k1, proj.k2, proj.k3, r2)\n}\n\nfunction LENS_DERIV(proj: GeoProj, r2: number): number {\n  return LENS_K(3.0 * proj.k1, 5.0 * proj.k2, 7.0 * proj.k3, r2)\n}\n\nfunction LENS_PX(proj: GeoProj, x: number, y: number): number {\n  return 1 + (2.0 * proj.p1 * y + proj.p2 * (x + 2.0 * y + y * y + 2.0 * x))\n}\n\nfunction LENS_PY(proj: GeoProj, LENS_PY_DERIV_X(proj: GeoProj, x: number, y: number): number {\n  return y * (2.0 * proj.p2 + proj.p1 * (2.0 + 2.0 * x))\n}\n\nfunction LENS_PY_DERIV_Y(proj: GeoProj, x: number, y: number): number {\n calculateInverseDistortion(\n  proj: GeoProj,\n  x: number,\n  y: number\n): [number, number, number] {\n  const xd = x\n  const yd = y\n  let xf = xd\n  let yf = yd\n\n  let i = 0\n  let diff1 = 1.0\n  while (i < 15 && diff1 > 1e-7) {\n    i += 1\n    const pxx = LENS_PX_DERIV_X(proj, xf, yf)\n    const pxy = LENS_PX_DERIV_Y(proj, xf, yf)\n    const pyx = LENS_PY_DERIV_X(proj, xf, yf)\n    const pyy = LENS_PY_DERIV_Y(proj, xf, yf)\n    const det = 1.0 / (pxx * pyy - pxy * pyx)\n    diff1 =\n      det *\n      (pyy * (xf * LENS_PX(proj, xf, yf) - xd) -\n        pxy * (yf * LENS_PY(proj, xf, yf) - yd))\n    const diff2 =\n      det *\n      (pxx * (yf * LENS_PY(proj, xf, yf) - yd) -\n        pyx * (xf * LENS_PX(proj, xf, yf) - xd))\n    xf -= diff1\n    yf -= diff2\n    diff1 = Math.max(Math.abs(diff1), Math.abs(diff2))\n  }\n  let c1 = 1.0\n  const r2 = xf * xf + yf * yf\n  i = 0\n  diff1 = 1.0\n  while (1 < 15 && Math.abs(diff1) > 1e-7) {\n    const ru2 = c1 * c1 * r2\n    diff1 = (c1 * LENS(proj, ru2) - 1) / LENS_DERIV(proj, ru2)\n    c1 -= diff1\n  }\n  return [xf, yf, c1]\n}\n\nexport function geoXYZToImcamMat(cam: GeoCamera): tmat4 {\n  let res = tmat4Identity()\n
